trans-unit.source: Enables service debugging for a [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] callback object.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer tjenesten feilsøking for en [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tilbakeringing objektet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The constructor creates a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior> object in which the value of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A> property is the value of `includeExceptionDetailInFaults`.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren oppretter en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior>objektet der verdien for den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A>egenskapen er verdien for `includeExceptionDetailInFaults`.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior>

trans-unit.source: Controls whether a [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] callback object includes managed exception information in the detail of the SOAP faults sent back to the service.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerer om en [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tilbakeringing tjenesteobjektet omfatter styrt unntaksinformasjon i detaljer om SOAP-feil som ble sendt tilbake til tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that controls whether client callback objects return managed exception information in SOAP faults back to the service.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som bestemmer om klienten tilbakeringing objekter returnere styrt unntaksinformasjon i SOAP-feil tilbake til tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] returns managed client callback exception information in the SOAP faults for service debugging purposes in duplex communication; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] returnerer administrert klienten tilbakeringing unntaksinformasjon i SOAP-feil for tjenesten feilsøkingsformål i duplekskommunikasjon; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Implements the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior.AddBindingParameters%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to support the behavior.
trans-unit.target: Implementerer den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior.AddBindingParameters%2A?displayProperty=fullName> metode for å støtte virkemåten.

trans-unit.target: Implementerer den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior.ApplyClientBehavior%2A?displayProperty=fullName> støtte virkemåten.

trans-unit.source: Assigns the value of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A> property to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Tilordner verdien for den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A>egenskapen til det <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.CallbackDebugBehavior.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A>
